OL,3,CUK enjoys hottest day of the year
OL,4,Cbefore cloudy skies return, Met Office
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FThe UK saw its hottest day of the year
OL,8,Fso far on Wednesday but cloudy skies
OL,9,Fand rain are expected to return later
OL,10,Fthis week, forecasters have said.
OL,12,FKew Gardens recorded the highest
OL,13,Ftemperature in the UK on Wednesday
OL,14,Fwith 18.7C, according to the Met
OL,15,FOffice.
OL,17,FThe forecaster said it is the highest
OL,18,Ftemperature recorded in the country in
OL,19,FFebruary since February 27 2019, when
OL,20,F19.2C was logged in Heathrow.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
