PN,31402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1772067789
OL,3,CUK enjoys hottest day of the year
OL,4,Cbefore cloudy skies return, Met Office
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FPrior to that, 21.2C was logged in Kew
OL,8,FGardens on February 26 the same year,
OL,9,Fwhich remains the highest temperature
OL,10,Frecorded in February in the UK.
OL,12,FBut the current spell of sunshine and
OL,13,Fdrier weather is not expected to last
OL,14,Fas temperatures are set to drop from
OL,15,FThursday.
OL,17,F"A brief period of southerly winds has
OL,18,Fdrawn in some warmer and drier air,"
OL,19,FDan Harris, chief forecaster at the
OL,20,FMet Office said earlier on Wednesday.
OL,26,@yD@AOUzD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
