PN,31404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1772067789
OL,3,CUK enjoys hottest day of the year
OL,4,Cbefore cloudy skies return, Met Office
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,F"This means a greater influence of
OL,8,Fmoister, Atlantic air, which is likely
OL,9,Fto be both cooler and contain more
OL,10,Fcloud."
OL,12,FOn Thursday, temperatures could reach
OL,13,Fhighs of 12C to 14C in most of England
OL,14,Fand Wales, 12C in Northern Ireland,
OL,15,Fand 10C to 11C in Scotland, according
OL,16,Fto the Met Office.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
