PN,31405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1772067789
OL,3,CUK enjoys hottest day of the year
OL,4,Cbefore cloudy skies return, Met Office
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FThe forecaster said there should be a
OL,8,F"bright start in the east", but skies
OL,9,Facross the country should be generally
OL,10,Fcloudy, with outbreaks of rain turning
OL,11,Fheavier and more persistent in the
OL,12,Fwest.
OL,14,FMany parts of the UK are expected to
OL,15,Fbe "unsettled with rain" on Friday,
OL,16,Fmaking way for some brighter spells on
OL,17,FSaturday, but with some showers.
OL,19,FCloud and rain will likely return from
OL,20,Fthe west on Sunday, according to the
OL,21,Fforecaster.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@ZO]wD@DOUwD@XO]
