OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1772067789
OL,3,CUK enjoys hottest day of the year
OL,4,Cbefore cloudy skies return, Met Office
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FThe UK has experienced a "lack of
OL,8,Fsunshine" over the winter months this
OL,9,Fyear, having had just 70% of its
OL,10,Faverage sunshine so far.
OL,12,FThe winter has also been particularly
OL,13,Fstormy and wet, with rainfall above
OL,14,Fthe average for the last 30 years.
OL,16,FThere are 41 flood warnings and 85
OL,17,Fflood alerts still in place across the
OL,18,FUK as of Wednesday, with most of them
OL,19,Fin Hampshire, Dorset, Wiltshire, and
OL,20,FSomerset.
OL,26,@oD@ZOUpD@IO]
